summary: WHILE DRIVING 35 MPH ANOTHER VEHICLE RAN A STOP SIGN.  THE CONSUMER APPLIED THE BRAKE BUT THE VEHICLE SKID ABOUT 15 FEET BEFORE HITTING A WALL. THE FRONT END WAS COMPLETED DAMAGED.  NEITHER AIR BAG DEPLOYED UPON IMPACT.  THE DRIVER SUFFERED SOME INJURIES.  THIS HAPPENED 13 APRIL 2003.  *NLM   *PH   *JB
